    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deck of Treads is a chaotic 2–6 player tank brawler with a deckbuilding twist. Stack upgrades that transform how your tank looks — and how it fights. Each match spirals into unpredictable mayhem, packed with ridiculous, over-the-top tank builds!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/573d9e2452f95653e06af32b94461d94.avif?t=1772395029\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades don’t just add to your tank — they <strong>stack</strong> and <strong>multiply</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Supercharge</strong> your shots, <strong>overclock</strong> your boosts, and <strong>amplify</strong> your shields… but be careful: some upgrades come with equally unhinged side effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/007701eac26f54089a257f7527fcfcfb.poster.avif?t=1772395029\" width=812 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/007701eac26f54089a257f7527fcfcfb.webm?t=1772395029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/51b6396fa0a3eeba982b4d8a31bb43b1.webp?t=1772395029\" width=100 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/e485a6047fe5753653976c32c4f29fb1.avif?t=1772395029\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll into battle with up to <strong>six players</strong> as each round gets <strong>faster</strong>, <strong>messier</strong>, and more <strong>chaotic</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shoot</strong>, <strong>Boost</strong>, and <strong>Shield</strong> your way to victory in both <strong>free-for-all</strong> and <strong>team</strong> battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/04d15018f2dcf7f24dd6afa0210377a0.poster.avif?t=1772395029\" width=812 height=267 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/04d15018f2dcf7f24dd6afa0210377a0.webm?t=1772395029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/51b6396fa0a3eeba982b4d8a31bb43b1.webp?t=1772395029\" width=100 height=25 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/6ca347b9a5b8c36d5778efe088efeeb4.avif?t=1772395029\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in a collection of unique<strong> </strong>arenas that demand constant strategic adaptation.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast away destructible objects to<strong> change the map layout</strong> over the course of a match.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate  active hazards like <strong>spinning blades</strong>, <strong>automatic doors, </strong>and <strong>explosive barrels, </strong>or use them to your advantage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/9b0c9472a4e8e3c72a1ea8c486d7027c.poster.avif?t=1772395029\" width=812 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321160/extras/9b0c9472a4e8e3c72a1ea8c486d7027c.webm?t=1772395029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
